{"tid":475951,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"各位絲打中意著咩波鞋？","createTime":"2017-11-21T14:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T05:17:53.000Z","uid":26519,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb3a4ee3ad78a9c176e57911bb74df481ce8156","tid":475951,"uid":26519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:40:31.000Z","msg":"由於我係學生哥一名 所以真係好中意著波鞋出街<br />\n又方便又舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n遲d出黎做野就應該唔可以日日著波鞋 依家真係要把握機會著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見討論波鞋既post多數都得巴打係度討論 唔知呢度有無絲打可以分享下你地著開既波鞋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5900a5796fe6c9e2380238802db297a5cd265c29","tid":475951,"uid":38591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e216ee3535eddc645717c687685c7db9bc32624f","tid":475951,"uid":26519,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/21/224211_db69e017852aa6c58eeaf00d85a56e98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F21%2F224211_db69e017852aa6c58eeaf00d85a56e98.jpg&h=022ed7de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢對adidas gazelle 襯衫唔錯 又多色揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一開始買個陣on9左要799 見而家500蚊都已經有交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51b3a423948fe2aa32f450cec2fb36820dd5b8c","tid":475951,"uid":31530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T14:44:51.000Z","msg":"converse啦"},{"pid